  FQM headquarters are in the city of Rio de Janeiro (Av.  
  José Silva de Azevedo Neto, 200, Condomínio O2 - Ed. Evolution II - 1º andar, Barra da Tijuca - Rio de Janeiro (RJ)).   
  Its manufacturing plant is located in the area of Jacaré in northern Rio de Janeiro. Divcom is headquartered in Recife (Av. Antônio de Góes, 275  9º. Andar Pina  Recife (PE)). It counts with a manufacturing plant (Vidfarma) in Pombos, located 65km from Recife and distribution centers in Campina Grande (Paraiba, Northeast Brazil). With the integration of both groups, the distribution of all pharmaceutical and dermacosmetics products will be concentrated in the distribution centers in Campina Grande (Paraiba).
